  "1698220": {
    "name": "Teslagrad 2",
    "steam_appid": 1698220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/ea7282710811932fccdc7b4e7ce7f7f5.avif?t=1725488586\" width=600 height=222 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索北方磁极的另一座高塔！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/2a52f1e3144a8b27d62218afeaff95c4.poster.avif?t=1725488586\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/2a52f1e3144a8b27d62218afeaff95c4.webm?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/2a52f1e3144a8b27d62218afeaff95c4.mp4?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>卢米娜，一个年轻的特斯拉法师，她的飞艇不幸坠落在维尔姆海姆，北方一个遥远而险恶的地区。为了脱困，她开启了一场危机重重的冒险，在峡湾山谷中，探索一个隐约可见的遗失的巨塔。玩家的任务是让卢米娜回家，与家人团聚。利用电磁力在荒芜的土地上生存。保护自己不受维京人的袭击，面对北欧神话中的可怕野兽，并战胜史诗般的大怪！随着旅程的进展，你将发现新的技能和装备，以揭开这片土地的秘密，并深入了解卢米娜先辈的黑暗历史。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/44551f78d7f72ef257ede378f1215e91.poster.avif?t=1725488586\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/44551f78d7f72ef257ede378f1215e91.webm?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/44551f78d7f72ef257ede378f1215e91.mp4?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《特斯拉学徒2》（Teslagrad 2）登场！这款《特斯拉学徒》的平台冒险游戏续作，包含磁力物理机制。续作中改进了视觉效果，增加了更大的世界场景，和新的谜题解决工具，游戏为玩家提供了一次新鲜的沉浸式解谜平台的体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/11032f7f459833007813d716b3d81933.poster.avif?t=1725488586\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/11032f7f459833007813d716b3d81933.webm?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/11032f7f459833007813d716b3d81933.mp4?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要特点：<br>•\t独特的氛围感！世界上首发朋克维京概念！一场宏大的蒸汽朋克与北欧文化碰撞的冒险，更有受北欧民间小调和电音启发的管弦乐背景音乐加持。<br>•\t探索！发掘绚烂精致的2D手绘场景，在满目疮痍的狂野世界中，寻找隐藏的道具、秘密和传说。<br>•\t磁力物理机制！以真实的电磁物理学为基础，用烧脑的谜题测试你的逻辑能力。享受磁极原理带来的新玩法。<br>•\t流体运动！在《特斯拉学徒1》的基础上掌握新技能。利用这些技能在世界中快速而熟练地移动，结合卢米娜的能力，如眨眼、滑动和磁化，建立额外的动力。<br>•\t史诗般的BOSS战！使用你的技能来对抗区域终区的BOSS战，从而解锁新的能力和更多的区域。<br>•\t视觉叙事手法！故事是通过你所看到的内容呈现出来的，没有文字、画外音或加载屏幕打断游戏体验。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/0135fea1b5022b552aa3ac4e5e7f1e14.poster.avif?t=1725488586\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/0135fea1b5022b552aa3ac4e5e7f1e14.webm?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698220/extras/0135fea1b5022b552aa3ac4e5e7f1e14.mp4?t=1725488586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
